                     <interp inst="t18370102-333-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18370102-cd-15" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370102-333-offence-1 t18370102-cd-15"></join>18th of December</rs>, 1 handkerchief, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18370102-name-194" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18370102-name-194" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
